Uses of Class
frogger.models.actors.Actor

Packages that use Actor 
Package Description
frogger.models.actors
A package of actors used as objects in a Level object for the Frogger Game adhering to the MVC design pattern.
frogger.models.levels
A package of levels for the Frogger Game adhering to the MVC design pattern.
